---
import SectionTitle from "./UI/SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section id="experience" class="section-padding bg-surface-100/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <SectionTitle title="Experience" />

    <div class="relative ml-4 border-l-2 border-primary/30 pl-8 md:ml-8 md:pl-12">
      <div class="reveal-up relative pb-12">
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+9px)] top-0 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-primary bg-surface md:-left-[calc(3rem+9px)]">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 animate-ping rounded-full bg-primary/40"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card p-6 md:p-8 glow-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white md:text-2xl">
                Software Developer
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-lg font-medium text-primary-light">
                Amdocs
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-primary-light">
                Full-time
              </span>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
                Jun 2024 &ndash; Present
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="mb-1 text-sm text-slate-500">
            Pune, Maharashtra, India &middot; On-site
          </p>

          <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Contributing to the <span class="text-white font-medium">RealTime Billing Product</span>,
              working on complex systems in a production-critical environment.
            </p>

            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-400">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
                Building and maintaining microservices using Java, Spring Boot, and Spring Framework
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
                Working with Apache Kafka and Confluent Kafka for real-time data streaming
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
                Managing data with Couchbase (including Capella) in distributed environments
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
                Deploying and orchestrating services with Kubernetes
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
                Implementing Aspect-Oriented Programming (AOP) and REST APIs
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
                Using Jira, TestNG, and Jenkins for development and delivery workflows
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {["Java", "Spring Boot", "Kafka", "Couchbase", "Kubernetes", "REST APIs", "AOP", "Microservices", "Jenkins"].map((tech) => (
              <span class="rounded-full bg-surface-300/50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-primary-light">
                {tech}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
